attributes.title: Retrieve All Logs
attributes.description: Displays all logs sorted by timestamp in ascending order.

kibanaSavedObjectMeta.searchSourceJSON: {"query": {"esql": "FROM unstructured-logs\n| where @timestamp >= now() - 1y // filter for logs from the last 1 year\n| sort @timestamp asc // sort logs by timestamp in ascending order"}, "index": {"id": "dbe3d33b8a15e80b61e4f52b8275675f49f957abaf82d186f114f1518eea4733", "title": "unstructured-logs", "timeFieldName": "@timestamp", "sourceFilters": [], "type": "esql", "fieldFormats": {}, "runtimeFieldMap": {}, "allowNoIndex": false, "name": "unstructured-logs", "allowHidden": false}, "filter": []}

attributes.title: Count Logs by Level
attributes.description: Counts the number of logs for each log level.

kibanaSavedObjectMeta.searchSourceJSON:
{"query": {"esql": "FROM unstructured-logs
| where @timestamp >= now() - 1y // filter for logs from the last 1 year
| stats count_all = count() by log.level // count logs grouped by log.level
| sort count_all desc // sort counts in descending order"}, "index": {"id": "dbe3d33b8a15e80b61e4f52b8275675f49f957abaf82d186f114f1518eea4733", "title": "unstructured-logs", "timeFieldName": "@timestamp", "sourceFilters": [], "type": "esql", "fieldFormats": {}, "runtimeFieldMap": {}, "allowNoIndex": false, "name": "unstructured-logs", "allowHidden": false}, "filter": []}

attributes.title: Retrieve Error Logs
attributes.description: Shows error logs with timestamp, source, and message.

kibanaSavedObjectMeta.searchSourceJSON:
{"query": {"esql": "FROM unstructured-logs
| where @timestamp >= now() - 1y // filter for logs from the last 1 year
| where log.level == "ERROR" // filter for error logs
| sort @timestamp desc // sort logs by timestamp in descending order
| keep @timestamp, source, message // keep only timestamp, source, and message fields"}, "index": {"id": "dbe3d33b8a15e80b61e4f52b8275675f49f957abaf82d186f114f1518eea4733", "title": "unstructured-logs", "timeFieldName": "@timestamp", "sourceFilters": [], "type": "esql", "fieldFormats": {}, "runtimeFieldMap": {}, "allowNoIndex": false, "name": "unstructured-logs", "allowHidden": false}, "filter": []}

attributes.title: Parse AuthService Logs with Dissect
attributes.description: Parses AuthService info logs using dissect to extract user and IP address.

kibanaSavedObjectMeta.searchSourceJSON:
{"query": {"esql": "FROM unstructured-logs
| where @timestamp >= now() - 1y // filter for logs from the last 1 year
| dissect message "User '%{user}' logged in successfully from IP address %{ip_address}" // extract user and ip_address from message using dissect
| where source == "AuthService" and log.level == "INFO" // filter for AuthService info logs
| sort @timestamp desc // sort logs by timestamp in descending order
| keep @timestamp, user, ip_address // keep only timestamp, user, and ip_address fields"}, "index": {"id": "dbe3d33b8a15e80b61e4f52b8275675f49f957abaf82d186f114f1518eea4733", "title": "unstructured-logs", "timeFieldName": "@timestamp", "sourceFilters": [], "type": "esql", "fieldFormats": {}, "runtimeFieldMap": {}, "allowNoIndex": false, "name": "unstructured-logs", "allowHidden": false}, "filter": []}

attributes.title: Parse AuthService Logs with Grok
attributes.description: Parses AuthService info logs using grok to extract user and IP address.

kibanaSavedObjectMeta.searchSourceJSON:
{"query": {"esql": "FROM unstructured-logs
| where @timestamp >= now() - 1y // filter for logs from the last 1 year
| grok message "User '%{USERNAME:user}' logged in successfully from IP address %{IP:ip_address}" // extract user and ip_address using grok
| where source == "AuthService" and log.level == "INFO" // filter for AuthService info logs
| sort @timestamp desc // sort logs by timestamp in descending order
| keep @timestamp, user, ip_address // keep only timestamp, user, and ip_address fields"}, "index": {"id": "dbe3d33b8a15e80b61e4f52b8275675f49f957abaf82d186f114f1518eea4733", "title": "unstructured-logs", "timeFieldName": "@timestamp", "sourceFilters": [], "type": "esql", "fieldFormats": {}, "runtimeFieldMap": {}, "allowNoIndex": false, "name": "unstructured-logs", "allowHidden": false}, "filter": []}
